Body: Description: I am getting the error message "The operation has timed out" on all of my permission scans today.  They scanned just fine on Friday. I checked the logs and there aren't any logs created for today, which makes me think it's something with the communication between the console and the proxy servers, but nothing changed between Friday and today.

I think this can be closed. most likely related to a server communication issue that was resolved post reboot.

If it reoccurs probably best to review event logs and any 3rd party applications that could interfere with process / traffic.
